snippet.title: ModNation Racers: Road Trip Feature Trailer - PS Vita
snippet.description:
Experience fun-filled kart racing at your fingertips! 

Speed off with a top class racing experience that's enhanced with PS Vita functions and is compatible with ModNation Racers on PlayStation 3.


Find out more about PS Vita
